OL,5, Thirty years after a brutal racist     
OL,6, attack that left Marlon Thomas in a    
OL,7, waking coma, his family say justice    
OL,8, still hasn't been served.              
OL,10,FMarlon, from Bristol, was 18 when he   
OL,11,Fwas attacked by a group of fairground  
OL,12,Fworkers on Durdham Downs in 1994,      
OL,13,Fleaving him permanently brain damaged. 
OL,15,FNow, his brother, Leroy, who makes     
OL,16,Fmusic under the name Rudey Lee, is     
OL,17,Freleasing an EP as a tribute.          
OL,19,FHe hopes the music will attract more   
OL,20,Fattention to what happened to Marlon.  
